俾你拎<br />\n一係夠鐘食飯直接擔遮出去食飯啦，唔通佢會搵老師攔住你咩。<br />\n最多番黎咪屌你兩句，記下過，唔通踢你出校咩。<br />\n好過on99敢怒不敢言，咁大個人高中生都唔識自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番學時期，個人生理需要食飯去廁所既時間咁撚重要，邊個阻住既就屌邊個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nband1仔嘛<br />\n奴性重，大人話乜就乜唔敢反抗<br />\n驚反抗就會被罰，記過<br />\n肚餓事小，操行紀錄留下污點事大"},{"pid":"1ece738b59a486cf9398be80cb0febae37ebb368","tid":258660,"uid":54424,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"係喎 七粒鐘之嘛 對比係大人即係兩日唔食都可以啦 我強烈建議話ok既人罰自己無野食無水飲兩日，千祈咪餓暈到要叫白車或食環就得"},{"pid":"7e643089234a0ad348d47972ebcef8679aa4792e","tid":258660,"uid":54424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"不覺講真 我寧願記小過理實得佢爬學校門走佬去食野"},{"pid":"fd56a6a702a9a7d80d4ae797918263c1b37f2fe0","tid":258660,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"仲以為70個鐘添<br />\n屌你7個鐘就暈有無咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba11f3d3764e12e9db376e6fb05c8102e1a7621","tid":258660,"uid":24634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"留名睇連登仔唔食野之餘割肉還母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇諗過人地身體唔舒服唔食野唔得呢？ <br />\n或者女學生咁岩黎m又冇野食真係會暈架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed7c11743ea02906c2c968c75773e82a0dc557a","tid":258660,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"c6da9a5bf8530faddb0fc0678fb34bcab27f74e8","tid":258660,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔d奴性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1e1cecc20aef5db77d19a80ddd12d5026e2761","tid":258660,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dca2b2b3bceeb2d44138a016c586c87c7acbc664","tid":258660,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed2cfc575ad2b7648ec0115fe9e60284b1a09d2f","tid":258660,"uid":48605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:33:46.000Z","msg":"咁大個人<br />\n暈咪報警call白車囉<br />\n餓到死都唔識反抗？"},{"pid":"54e894e29439025b0c9e46ef12639a39d80fcfde","tid":258660,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"小食部有咩食先？唔知有咩點討論<br />\n<br />\n唔食早餐嗰d人，唔食野18個鐘都得啦，等多三個鐘算得係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8892ac879325469f66f34022054ae9e371120788","tid":258660,"uid":117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 7粒鐘啫...<br />\n唔係話單嘢冇問題<br />\n但係7粒鐘真係好小事</blockquote><br />\n報紙佬寫誇d, 好正常。</blockquote><br />\n7個鐘係assume左佢地食左早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估個個有早餐食/食得飽?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好多人朝頭早食個空心包咁就返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔食早餐先正常，食完早餐頂住個胃，lunch食完肚腩會大</blockquote><br />\n我敢講至少有一半中學生都係空肚/食舊包番學<br />\n咁計法當佢8點dinner<br />\n3點半放學先有野食<br />\n即係差唔多20個鐘冇野食<br />\n咁都叫好小事我唔知咩叫大事喇"},{"pid":"e0e90cd4baa8eb0dade72c349af5ecd253889052","tid":258660,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小食部有咩食先？唔知有咩點討論<br />\n<br />\n唔食早餐嗰d人，唔食野18個鐘都得啦，等多三個鐘算得係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原文講到話連課室都唔准離開"},{"pid":"6391707169981c96ad34861ed79004f4a7863432","tid":258660,"uid":54424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好大件事，只係校方做法不合理<br />\n如果真係做教育既，面對青春期既學生無得食自己仲係出便開心歡暢食野？<br />\n青春期最需要營養既時候，講真上左咁耐堂攰同肚餓好正常，無食野叫佢地淨係買小食部啲食物食，唔係好係路囉<br />\n學校真係無錢到一日半日去提供番食物俾班後生都唔得咩？<br />\n又或者例係死既人係生既咪去附近屯碼果邊<br />\n搵野番學校俾班後生囉！我諗唔會無食肆做生意掛？<br />\n<br />\n黃雨啫？驚學生危險但係又唔俾食野係咩玩法？肚餓可以專心到讀書？"},{"pid":"ce699d881ca8e8943501e58ac4712934056f4b74","tid":258660,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"而家啲00後返學竟然要食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5af4e10c9e54aa2298d2c2a3402fe849a8516f","tid":258660,"uid":4607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 7粒鐘啫...<br />\n唔係話單嘢冇問題<br />\n但係7粒鐘真係好小事</blockquote><br />\n報紙佬寫誇d, 好正常。</blockquote><br />\n7個鐘係assume左佢地食左早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估個個有早餐食/食得飽?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家學校唔俾佢地食早餐咩<br />\n自己選擇唔食又入學校數</blockquote><br />\n邊個話入學校數？<br />\n而家係解釋緊點解唔食lunch會餓暈"},{"pid":"e1e771ae795bb1d2a53d67af6958fd36f65c282d","tid":258660,"uid":4607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係個一種自己挨到，其他人挨唔到就係有問題既精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左考慮少左冇食早餐既人，有無考慮本身體質欠佳例如貧血人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有d上完pe堂無飯食"},{"pid":"34940843cd4599380ac18e03548b42381363c0fe","tid":258660,"uid":61516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"唔屌班教畜屌學生<br />\n同香討班盲毛廢中有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a16821beadd55fa4130364332887b5b48c94f9","tid":258660,"uid":4607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前中學都係唔食早餐，寧願訓多陣，好多人都係咁 反而會食早餐係少數<br />\n<br />\n保守咁計落當由前一晚9點食完飯到第二日放學冇食過嘢都有18個鐘 好難唔暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就算正常12點食飯都要捱15個鐘啦，再多3個鐘就頂唔住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1530放學就即走咩<br />\n唔俾人要補課呀有其他課外活動架咩"},{"pid":"4c2d6c968c48e9cee881ff99e5e10f495c2b89cc","tid":258660,"uid":53057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，點解餓到喊，餓到暈都唔肯食小食部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cf6a888e05b0e7f14406585e6ab13d50239b31","tid":258660,"uid":35178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"咁多人成日話以前點點點唔食，你地咪同班老屎忽一樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5b27804404747df7de89d4a414d46c185040b1","tid":258660,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"血糖低 嚴重既話後果都幾大獲<br />\n奴性重還奴性重啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699ce4d738e62c4adff40eff6dbfcca0608119fa","tid":258660,"uid":59695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 7粒鐘啫...<br />\n唔係話單嘢冇問題<br />\n但係7粒鐘真係好小事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十幾歲細路新陳代謝率快你呢條幾十勾人妖一大截<br />\n又唔係好似你呢啲廢柴咁成日無飯開捱慣餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會暈好奇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47043f9e49001b